---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Engagement Agreement · Pro Se Fair Play Mediation"
  description="The Engagement Agreement governing services with Pro Se Fair Play Mediation, LLC. Provided here for reference; opens in a new tab from the payment page."
  noindex
>
  <header class="legal-header">
    <div class="container legal-header-inner">
      <p class="kicker reveal reveal-d1">
        <a href="/pay" class="back-link">
          <span class="arrow-left" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
          Back to payment
        </a>
        <span class="kicker-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        Reference
      </p>
      <h1 class="display legal-title reveal reveal-d2">
        Engagement <span class="display-italic">Agreement</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lede reveal reveal-d3">
        Please review carefully before checking the agreement box on
        the payment page. A downloadable PDF and Word copy are also
        available on the <a class="link-underline" href="/legal/terms">Agreement</a> page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container-narrow legal-prose">
      <div class="agreement-meta">
        <p class="agreement-tagline">Where We Level the Playing Field</p>
        <address class="agreement-contact">
          700 South Rosemary Avenue, Suite 204<br />
          West Palm Beach, Florida 33401<br />
          <a href="tel:+15619410896">(561) 941-0896</a><br />
          <a href="mailto:info@prosefairplaymediation.com">info@prosefairplaymediation.com</a><br />
          <a href="https://www.prosefairplaymediation.com">www.prosefairplaymediation.com</a>
        </address>
        <p class="agreement-stamp">Confidential Client Engagement Document</p>
        <p class="agreement-preface">
          This Agreement contains important terms and conditions
          regarding mediation and document preparation services. Please
          review carefully before signing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-h2">1. Nature of Services</h2>
      <p>
        Pro Se Fair Play Mediation LLC provides mediation, neutral
        facilitation, family mediation, high-conflict dispute
        facilitation, document preparation services for self-represented
        individuals, administrative support services, parenting plan
        drafting assistance based solely upon client-provided
        information, court form preparation services, and scheduling
        assistance.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Company is not a law firm and does not provide legal advice
        or legal representation.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">2. No Attorney-Client Relationship</h2>
      <p>
        No attorney-client relationship is created by this Agreement.
        Clients are encouraged to seek independent legal counsel
        regarding their legal rights and obligations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">3. Mediation Services</h2>
      <p>
        The mediator acts solely as a neutral facilitator and does not
        advocate for either party. No guarantees regarding settlement
        or outcomes are made.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">4. Confidentiality</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted under Florida law, mediation
        communications shall remain confidential pursuant to Chapter
        44, Florida Statutes, and applicable Florida mediation rules.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">5. Document Preparation Services</h2>
      <p>
        The Company acts solely as a scrivener and administrative
        preparer. All information inserted into forms or documents is
        supplied by the Client.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">6. Fees and Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>
        All fees are earned upon commencement of services unless
        otherwise agreed in writing. Additional charges may apply for
        rush services, revisions, administrative support, or
        rescheduled sessions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">7. No Guarantee of Results</h2>
      <p>
        The Company makes no guarantees regarding mediation outcomes,
        judicial rulings, settlement terms, or litigation results.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, the Company's total
        liability shall not exceed the amount actually paid by Client
        for services rendered.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">9. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>
        Any dispute arising under this Agreement shall first be
        submitted to mediation in Palm Beach County, Florida. Florida
        law shall govern this Agreement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-h2">10. Important Legal Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        Pro Se Fair Play Mediation LLC is not a law firm. We are not
        attorneys and do not provide legal advice or legal
        representation. We provide mediation and document preparation
        services for self-represented individuals only.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-header {
    position: relative;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 6vw + 1rem, 6rem) clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(196, 154, 75, 0.08), transparent 55%),
      var(--color-cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-header-inner { position: relative; max-width: 64rem; }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-navy); }
  .arrow-left { transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out); }
  .back-link:hover .arrow-left { transform: translateX(-3px); }
  .kicker-sep { color: var(--color-divider); margin-inline: 0.4rem; }
  .legal-title {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .legal-title .display-italic {
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .legal-header .lede {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .legal-body {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-3xl);
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .legal-prose {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
  .legal-prose p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .legal-prose strong { color: var(--color-navy); font-weight: 600; }
  .legal-prose a {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    background-image: linear-gradient(var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold));
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100% 1px;
    background-position: 0 92%;
  }
  .legal-prose a:hover { color: var(--color-gold-deep); }

  .agreement-meta {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .agreement-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .agreement-contact {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .agreement-stamp {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .agreement-preface {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .section-h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    position: relative;
  }
  .section-h2::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px; left: 0;
    width: 2.5rem; height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .legal-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 1.8rem + 3vw, 3.5rem); }
    .section-h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 2vw, 2.25rem); }
  }
</style>
